rComments: I took this class in September of 2020. Professor Campagnolo was a great teacher, all of his information was very clear, and his lectures were easy to follow! He is also very nice and always willing to answer questions. I would take a course from him again. I would recommend to other students to go to all of his lectures, as they were very helpful!

I took this class during COVID which posed some problems in and of itself but Prof Campagnolo adapted very well. He answers questions with great detail and has lots of patience for follow up questions. He is the single most organized prof I have ever had. He is a bit dry but is very clear and concise, overall he's a great prof.

rComments: I took his Legislation class during the COVID-19 pandemic. Final exam was 100% of course mark. He was superbly organised, and answered questions clearly and quickly.
